## Prerequisites

Before configuring or launching the service, ensure the following requirements are met:

### System Requirements
- **Operating System**: Windows 10/11 or Windows Server 2016+
- **Architecture**: x64 (64-bit)
- **Permissions**: Administrator rights (required to bind ports and register services)

### Dependencies
- [Windows Runtime](https://www.microsoft.com/es-es/download/details.aspx?id=39717)
- [Microsoft SQL Server 2017+](https://www.microsoft.com/es-es/evalcenter/download-sql-server-2017-rtm)
- [ODBC Driver 17 for SQL Server](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/sql/connect/odbc/download-odbc-driver-for-sql-server?view=sql-server-ver17)

